column2: can't remember the last time i slept
i unnecessarily wipe for 20 minutes until i'm practically bleeding
makes me a little less nauseous
making myself get out of bed
feel like i have super powers
before i do anything else stupid
pain in the pit of my stomach
cant shut up for the whole day
hasn't stopped shaking her leg the entire hour
makes me act like a devil
my adderall got cut in half and now i'm dying
top of my femur got fractured
it's feeling like the same day
screwing with my short term memory
